00:16:30.889 --> 00:16:33.892
And so this particular
animation

00:16:33.892 --> 00:16:37.162
is going to cast a light on
how we can go about,

00:16:37.162 --> 00:16:40.666
you know, funding and helping
their efforts on the fields.

